body_html:
Ubuntu 18.04 is default Python 3.6, meaning if we move to that as the base we would need to switch the default as part of the DockerFile to Python 2.x for the python 2.x build

What I should have said above is that the default python3 version in 18.04 went from 3.5 to 3.6.
